阮文祿以'''山卿'''（Sơn Khanh）爲筆名進行文學創作，作品有：<ref>{{Cite web |title=Đến với Sơn Khanh một giờ - Tuyển tập Nguyễn Văn Sâm |url=https://www.namkyluctinh.org/tuyen-tap/nguyen-van-sam/tuyen-tap/van-hoc---bien-khao/dhen-voi-son-khanh-mot-gio.html |website=www.namkyluctinh.org |access-date=2022-06-19 |archive-date=2022-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220620033754/https://www.namkyluctinh.org/tuyen-tap/nguyen-van-sam/tuyen-tap/van-hoc---bien-khao/dhen-voi-son-khanh-mot-gio.html }}</ref>

