== 家庭 ==
阮文祿的胞弟阮文長（<span lang="vi" dir="ltr">Nguyễn Văn Trường</span>）教授是越南教育家，曾擔任越南共和國教育部長，2018年逝世於美國休斯頓。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web |author=THANH PHONG |date=2018-01-28 |title=Lễ tưởng niệm GS. Nguyễn Văn Trường, Nguyên Bộ Trưởng Bộ Quốc Gia Giáo Dục VNCH |url=http://viendongdaily.com/le-tuong-niem-gs-nguyen-van-truong-nguyen-bo-truong-bo-quoc-gia-giao-duc-N2ZG7HSW.html |website=viendongdaily.com |access-date=2022-06-20 |archive-date=2018-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201024136/http://viendongdaily.com/le-tuong-niem-gs-nguyen-van-truong-nguyen-bo-truong-bo-quoc-gia-giao-duc-N2ZG7HSW.html }}</ref>

阮文祿去世時留下了妻子和四個子女，最小的2歲，最大的7歲。<ref name=":1" />

